ar y las facilidades que te ofrecen. Un 10 se queda corto. Gracias a las dos","time":1685960898,"translated":false},{"author_name":"STELLA GUERRERO","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110483821064843781499/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AD_cMMSNyljR8NAdT-XmJNYidT0ke7gzp9_hbru6q657Wg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 3 semanas","text":"Ya he visitado varias veces este sitio y lo que más me gusta es la atención del personal en especial de Andrea que se toma todo el tiempo preciso  para explicar hasta el último detalle , muy buen servicio","time":1684832636,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sandra Hernández Moreno","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104357108627187734215/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTte6uiFkGenajjh3jzI9se71HiPqNK5SHZYefxkc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"en la última semana","text":"Fuimos a cambiar divisas, trato fenomenal, clara información, personal muy amable. Y además buen cambio. Sin duda, repetiré en mis próximas veces. Recomendado 100x100.","time":1686584921,"translated":false}],"types":["jewelry_store","finance","point_of_interest","store","establishment"],"url":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=13882353097699614927","user_ratings_total":425,"utc_offset":120,"vicinity":"Avenida de Andalucía, 18, Sevilla","website":"https://quickgold.es/tiendas/compro-oro-sevilla/avenida-de-andalucia-18/?utm_source=gmb&utm_medium=boton&utm_content&utm_campaign=sitio-web-gmb","wheelchair_accessible_entrance":true},"status":"OK"},"tienda2Google":{"html_attributions":[],"result":{"address_components":[{"long_name":"43","short_name":"43","types":["street_number"]},{"long_name":"Calle San Eloy","short_name":"C. San Eloy","types":["route"]},{"long_name":"Sevilla","short_name":"Sevilla","types":["locality","polit